:48.000Z","msg":"如果平時打蚊我就會一掌拍落隻蚊，將佢拍向牆or 地下， 咁隻蚊就會暈，到時慢慢踩死佢或者用紙巾㩒死佢，夠乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1688f5c4e33bb52e1ddfa6928d93c02335ffa923","tid":1992203,"uid":327354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"誘敵法<br />\n蚊鍾意咬腳<br />\n攞隻腳出黎引佢<br />\n隻蚊實忍唔住"},{"pid":"f7b8c1a04726a1c27c66c0fc2458e8bfb52aa96b","tid":1992203,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"用手向正前方抓"},{"pid":"316976555e0d91961159c4784a3b54ee638182fb","tid":1992203,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0376c487c5e04586fdb3fc77a598c33550b9dde3","tid":1992203,"uid":81880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"電蚊拍 so far ok,<br />\n<br />\n想問電子滅蚊液有無用 會唔會對人體有害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"好有用<br />\n開左唔會有蚊 (本身勁惹蚊)<br />\n唔好閂晒門窗咁用 你會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我開窗開風扇, 用左十年八年 都無副作用/不良反應"},{"pid":"03215e4dbab1fd9b2c7ba0251cc6438b0aa98fad","tid":1992203,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"霧夜飛鷹 無影手"},{"pid":"46ed07cbf5de9564f50f6feaa9e6e8e52adb18aa","tid":1992203,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"316976555e0d91961159c4784a3b54ee638182fb","tid":1992203,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0376c487c5e04586fdb3fc77a598c33550b9dde3","tid":1992203,"uid":81880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"電蚊拍 so far ok,<br />\n<br />\n想問電子滅蚊液有無用 會唔會對人體有害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"好有用<br />\n開左唔會有蚊 (本身勁惹蚊)<br />\n唔好閂晒門窗咁用 你會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我開窗開風扇, 用左十年八年 都無副作用/不良反應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"唔知對寵物有冇害"},{"pid":"437c735936ab5a4bc9ea6a495b